replyContent:
Hi Kevin,
Old versions (2.x) is completely broken, it's not able stream music anymore, so I have to make the update mandatory.
And about auto tagging, you're right, it's not accurate. I'm trying to implement a better way (flow) for it, but since it's quite complicated, it will take time. Thanks for your feedback.
